  of hvkInt:
      intVal*: int

  of hvkStr:
      strVal*: string

  of hvkFloat:
      floatVal*: float

  of hvkBool:
      boolVal*: bool

  of hvkRefBox:
      refBox*: int

  of hvkRecord:
